text: Stan Sohler aka Jayson Loam writing at a California nudist camp for a nudist magazine Photo by Ed Lange (1958). This photo gets passed around a lot as being J D Salinger.
J.D. Salinger writing at a nudist getaway. Inspiration is everywhere, I guess! pic.twitter.com/5e0nEOCXOA
